## Типичные паттерны

### Таблица с пагинацией

```jinja2
{% import 'components.html' as c %}

{% call c.card(title='Сессии (' + total|string + ')') %}
    {{ c.counter_badge(sessions|length) }}
{% endcall %}

<div class="card-body p-0">
    {% if sessions %}
        {% call c.table_container(min_width='1000px') %}
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Платформа</th>
                    <th>Статус</th>
                    <th>Сообщений</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {% for session in sessions %}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{ c.platform_badge(session.platform) }}</td>
                    <td>{{ c.status_badge(session.status) }}</td>
                    <td>{{ c.counter_badge(session.message_count) }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        {% endcall %}
        
        <div class="card-footer">
            {{ c.pagination(offset, limit, total, '/api/sessions') }}
        </div>
    {% else %}
        {{ c.empty_state(icon='inbox', title='Нет сессий') }}
    {% endif %}
</div>
```

